<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Comment ça marche - VoteZ</title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/21.png" type="image/x-icon">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* Fond animé */
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #f8f9fa, #e0f7fa, #ffe6f0, #d2dff3);
      background-size: 400% 400%;
      animation: gradientBG 15s ease infinite;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    @keyframes gradientBG {
      0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
      50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #333;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .steps-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .step-card {
      position: relative;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }

    .step-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }

    .step-icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      color: #00bcd4;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .step-card:hover .step-icon {
      transform: rotate(10deg) scale(1.2);
    }

    .step-number {
      position: absolute;
      top: -15px;
      left: -15px;
      background-color: #ff4081;
      color: #fff;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 50%;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .step-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .step-desc {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Bouton retour accueil */
    .btn-home {
      display: block;
      margin: 50px auto 0 auto;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      border-radius: 12px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
      background-color: #00bcd4;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .btn-home:hover {
      background-color: #007c91;
      transform: scale(1.05);
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .step-card {
        padding: 20px 15px;
      }
      .step-icon {
        font-size: 3rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>Comment ça marche ?</h1>

  <div class="steps-container">
    <div class="step-card">
      <div class="step-number">1</div>
      <i class="bi bi-person-circle step-icon"></i>
      <div class="step-title">Inscription</div>
      <div class="step-desc">
        Créez votre compte rapidement avec votre email et mot de passe. 
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-card">
      <div class="step-number">2</div>
      <i class="bi bi-card-checklist step-icon"></i>
      <div class="step-title">Choisissez votre candidat</div>
      <div class="step-desc">
        Parcourez la liste des candidats et sélectionnez celui que vous soutenez.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-card">
      <div class="step-number">3</div>
      <i class="bi bi-check2-square step-icon"></i>
      <div class="step-title">Votez</div>
      <div class="step-desc">
        Validez votre vote en toute sécurité. Chaque utilisateur ne peut voter qu'une seule fois.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-card">
      <div class="step-number">4</div>
      <i class="bi bi-bar-chart-line step-icon"></i>
      <div class="step-title">Consultez les résultats</div>
      <div class="step-desc">
        Visualisez les résultats en temps réel grâce à notre graphique interactif et coloré.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a href="/" class="btn btn-home">Retour à l'accueil</a>

</body>
</html>
